Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.73,0:01:02.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NWhy is Nishiyama here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.52,0:01:04.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NWhy is Hayama here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.02,0:01:07.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA] Are those tears?\NHayama's crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.65,0:01:09.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NThat was strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.15,0:01:12.11,Main,,0,0,0,,She's all alone.\NI wonder what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:13.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NHere!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.07,0:01:54.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA cooing, giggling]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.16,0:01:57.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, now. Let's all\Nplay nice, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.33,0:01:59.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I've got plenty of\Nlove for everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.66,0:02:02.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama, your drink's\Nready whenever you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.79,0:02:05.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:07.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Kono's gotten\Nso big, hasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.88,0:02:10.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[laughs] She's quite the\Nlittle troublemaker now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.59,0:02:11.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[door opens]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.97,0:02:15.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Tricky Cat!\NIs a counter seat all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.38,0:02:16.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NSure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:35.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NHey, sleepyhead! You awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.16,0:02:37.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I've got a surprise for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:40.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA yawns]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:44.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU giggling]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.88,0:02:48.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU] I found a shop I\Nthink you're gonna like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:50.29,Main,,0,0,0,,It should be just up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:52.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah? What kind\Nof place is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:54.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.26,0:02:56.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I think it's absolutely\Nperfect for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.47,0:02:58.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:03:00.06,Main,,0,0,0,,No! I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:01.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I would be cheating on Bel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:03.35,Main,,0,0,0,,It's cruel to\Ntempt me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:05.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Relax. We'll just hang\Nout for a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:07.02,Main,,0,0,0,,You know you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:13.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NHere. Might as well use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.53,0:03:16.70,Main,,0,0,0,,So you were already\Nplanning to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:20.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I heard about it a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:22.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I wish you had told me this\Nwas where we were going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:24.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:25.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted it to be\Na surprise for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:27.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NI don't have my camera,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:29.38,Main,,0,0,0,,so I'll have to use my\Npotato of a cellphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.46,0:03:31.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Poor baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.38,0:03:33.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NWhy is Nishiyama here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:35.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NWhy is Hayama here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.38,0:03:37.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] This was supposed to\Nbe a special experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:39.51,Main,,0,0,0,,She's going to ruin it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:42.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Look! It's your friend.\NThe one we saw at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:44.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello.\NNice to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:47.35,Main,,0,0,0,,That's Nishiyama.\NAnd she's just a classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:48.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.98,0:03:50.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Weren't you one of the people\Nwho helped Teru out before?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:52.48,Main,,0,0,0,,You adopted one of\Nthe abandoned kittens
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:53.73,Main,,0,0,0,,that she found, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.82,0:03:55.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:56.57,Main,,0,0,0,,That's so sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:58.11,Main,,0,0,0,,So what did you\Nend up naming her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.20,0:04:00.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh. I guess I forgot to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:02.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Gimme a break. Like you care.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.87,0:04:04.45,Main,,0,0,0,,We named ours\NLittle Beelzebub.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:05.91,Main,,0,0,0,,You know, like the\Nlord of the flies,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:07.46,Main,,0,0,0,,'cause the poor thing\Nwas swarming with them
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:08.41,Main,,0,0,0,,when we found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:09.92,Main,,0,0,0,,It's Bel for short, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:11.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted my little one\Nto have a name
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:13.25,Main,,0,0,0,,that reflects my undying love,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:16.09,Main,,0,0,0,,so I decided to call her\NEternal. She's "El" for short.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:17.92,Main,,0,0,0,,--[HAYAMA giggles]\N--[NISHIYAMA] What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:20.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Nothing. That's a\Nvery creative name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:25.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Yep. I can just imagine you\Npouring through a thesaurus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.85,0:04:27.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NHey, Teru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:30.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Have you heard the names of all\Nthe kitties they've got here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:32.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Princess Konohana Sakuya,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:36.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Lakshmi, Viracocha,\Nand Teutates.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:39.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a little much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:40.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I like their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:42.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I think they're\Nrefined and regal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:44.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Or ridiculous.\NThink about it for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:47.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you wanna be out in public\Ntalking about your cat
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:49.87,Main,,0,0,0,,"Princess Konohana Sakuya"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.96,0:04:51.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, you can think\Nwhatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:54.21,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not like I came here\Nto talk to you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:57.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I've got better things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:59.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Like play with\Nsweet little kitties!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:01.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHOP WORKER]\NHey Nishiyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:03.85,Main,,0,0,0,,It's good to see you again.\NHow are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:05.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Good, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.14,0:05:06.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm really glad\Nto see Mi here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:08.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I've missed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:09.60,Main,,0,0,0,,She wasn't around\Nthe last time I came,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.68,0:05:11.02,Main,,0,0,0,,so I was getting worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:12.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHOP WORKER]\NIt's so sweet of you to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:13.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Listen to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:16.94,Main,,0,0,0,,It sounds like she's kind\Nof a regular around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.02,0:05:20.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] I'm not jealous.\NNot even a little bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:22.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NOh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:23.20,Main,,0,0,0,,That's kinda random.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:25.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, running\Ninto her like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:27.20,Main,,0,0,0,,It isn't that surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:30.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Hmm... I wonder\Nhow I could convince her
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:31.62,Main,,0,0,0,,to send me those pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:33.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NI have something for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:35.58,Main,,0,0,0,,but if you've already gotten\Nyour fix at the cat café...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:37.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.09,0:05:39.30,Main,,0,0,0,,A ticket to Animal Town.\NY'know, that petting zoo place?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:40.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NWhat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:42.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Give it to me!\NI'll do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.43,0:05:44.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NOkay, calm down. It's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:47.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Sakura's mom actually\Ngave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:49.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I figured you'd appreciate\Nit a lot more than I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:51.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NThis is awesome! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.89,0:05:54.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey, it says it's\Ngood for two people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:56.90,Main,,0,0,0,,So when do you\Nthink we should go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:59.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Looks like it's\Ngood till Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.53,0:06:01.78,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll have to buy one ticket,\Nsince there are three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:03.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I wasn't gonna go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:06.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't like animals\Nall that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.32,0:06:07.37,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:09.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't go either. I'm working.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:11.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NReally? You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:14.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, maybe you could\Nbring your sister along.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:16.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I dunno about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:18.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Yay! Let's have some fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:20.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, Teru?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:22.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Sis, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.26,0:06:24.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw! Who's a little cutie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:26.76,Main,,0,0,0,,You have to be gentler\Nwith the little ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.85,0:06:28.93,Main,,0,0,0,,This one is adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:30.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw! And so is that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:31.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Take a deep breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:35.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Slow down and adore\Nthem one at a time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:37.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Going with Kou would\Nbe too exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:41.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd have to protect all\Nthe animals from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:43.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:45.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NAnimal Town?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:46.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:49.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoko and I can't go, but we\Nthought you might want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.12,0:06:50.08,Main,,0,0,0,,What do ya say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:51.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Me? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:52.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:55.25,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?\NI don't wanna go with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:57.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I think she'd like it.\NDon't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:07:00.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Besides, you went to\Nthe cat café together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:02.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] We definitely\Ndid not go there together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.80,0:07:05.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA] I have a feeling\Nthis isn't going to end well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:14.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.31,0:07:17.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Back at ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:20.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Nishiyama showed!\NI can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.15,0:07:22.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought Hayama had\Nscared her off for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:24.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Their love for animals\Nmust be stronger
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:25.90,Main,,0,0,0,,than their hatred for each other
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.99,0:07:28.32,Main,,0,0,0,,You came too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:29.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Checking up on them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.62,0:07:32.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO] Well, yeah.\NYou know how they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:33.66,Main,,0,0,0,,They're going in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.75,0:07:35.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I gotta see how this ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.38,0:07:44.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Animal Town!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:48.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:50.97,Main,,0,0,0,,This is gonna be a\Nlong day, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.05,0:07:53.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NHey sweetie! Look over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:55.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA squeals]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:58.60,Main,,0,0,0,,You pups have a very\Nimportant job, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:08:01.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes! You're the first thing\Npeople see when they walk in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:03.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you for\Nall your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:04.69,Main,,0,0,0,,You're doing great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:07.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO] They've been\Nat it for ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:08.74,Main,,0,0,0,,When are they gonna move on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:10.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NI don't know, but at this rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:12.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama's going\Nto run out of memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:19.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NJust because we came in together
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.42,0:08:21.38,Main,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean we\Nhave to stay together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:24.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't see any reason\Nwhy we can't split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.84,0:08:26.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.26,0:08:28.43,Main,,0,0,0,,The small animals are closest,\Nso I'll go there first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:29.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Then the dog show.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:32.35,Main,,0,0,0,,After that, the cat room,\Nthe small dog petting corner,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:35.76,Main,,0,0,0,,the exotic animal show,\Nand the horse park.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:37.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, see ya later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:39.73,Main,,0,0,0,,We're probably better off\Ngoing our own ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:41.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure, fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:45.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NNo way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:47.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Did she plan out\Nthe same route I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:51.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[STAFF]\NJump and catch! Good boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:53.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's give Jack\Na hand, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:56.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow! Good boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:59.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA] Are those tears?\NHayama's crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:01.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know why\Nso many people
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:03.25,Main,,0,0,0,,have children when\Nthey could have dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:05.54,Main,,0,0,0,,A puppy is just as cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.63,0:09:07.42,Main,,0,0,0,,In fact, I'd say\Nthat they're cuter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:10.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I think that's taking it a\Nlittle too far, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:16.97,Main,,0,0,0,,So I guess they decided\Nto stick together after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.06,0:09:20.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Think they'll be okay?\NThings could get violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:22.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, Hayama will\Nbehave herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:23.81,Main,,0,0,0,,She won't start a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:25.19,Main,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:27.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Because she made a vow\Nto exercise self-discipline.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.61,0:09:28.94,Main,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:30.49,Main,,0,0,0,,She said she wants\Nto open herself up
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:33.37,Main,,0,0,0,,to new experiences by being\Nmore tolerant of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:35.78,Main,,0,0,0,,And I think there was\Nsomething about inner peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:38.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, sure.\NI'll pretend that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:39.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:41.62,Main,,0,0,0,,If Nishiyama deliberately\Nprovokes her,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:43.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know what could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:44.75,Main,,0,0,0,,She might crack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:46.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NOver here, little cutie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:48.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, Nishiyama.\NYou're really good at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:50.72,Main,,0,0,0,,You've got them hooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:52.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:53.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought it was something\Nthat came naturally
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.47,0:09:54.89,Main,,0,0,0,,to all cat owners,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:57.35,Main,,0,0,0,,but I guess you must not have\Nthe knack for it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:09:58.97,Main,,0,0,0,,You know,\Nyou're probably right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:00.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I should practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:02.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NWhat did you get to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.27,0:10:03.52,Main,,0,0,0,,It looks like juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:05.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I decided to get tea instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:09.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't think juice is healthy\Nbecause of all the sugar in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:11.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow!\NYou're being so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:15.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I wish I had that\Nmuch discipline.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:16.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NThat one there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:18.58,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a Weimaraner,\Nalso known as the "Gray Ghost"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:20.58,Main,,0,0,0,,because of the color\Nof its coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:23.83,Main,,0,0,0,,You mean you seriously\Ndidn't know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.91,0:10:25.21,Main,,0,0,0,,That's really amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:27.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Is there anything you\Ndon't know about animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:29.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I am fairly knowledgeable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.63,0:10:32.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA] I don't get it.\NShe's being so nice today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.63,0:10:33.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I've never seen her like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:36.76,Main,,0,0,0,,It's almost like somebody else\Nhas taken over her body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:38.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:40.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama's not holding\Nanything back, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:43.73,Main,,0,0,0,,The dam is gonna break\Nany second now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:45.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO]\NAh! Can't she see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:48.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:50.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Today's going a lot better\Nthan I thought it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.77,0:10:52.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Being around you isn't\Nas painful as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:54.40,Main,,0,0,0,,It's almost fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:10:59.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.53,0:11:01.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah? What?\NSomething wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:05.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:11.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:17.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA crying]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:19.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NWhat is Hayama's problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.93,0:11:21.76,Main,,0,0,0,,She seemed totally\Nnormal all day,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:24.52,Main,,0,0,0,,and then out of nowhere,\Nshe said those awful things!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:25.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I hate her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.61,0:11:32.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NDid you come to cheer me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:34.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[meows]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:37.32,Main,,0,0,0,,You're so sweet.\NThank you, El!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:39.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] Did you have\Nfun at Animal Town?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:41.58,Main,,0,0,0,,It was a lot of fun, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:43.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to go back sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.29,0:11:45.04,Main,,0,0,0,,And spending the day\Nwith Nishiyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:47.00,Main,,0,0,0,,How did things go\Nbetween the two of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:48.54,Main,,0,0,0,,You know, same as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:49.71,Main,,0,0,0,,About halfway through the day,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:52.29,Main,,0,0,0,,she got angry for\Nsome reason and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:54.05,Main,,0,0,0,,It seemed like she\Nwas having a good time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:56.26,Main,,0,0,0,,and there was still\Na lot left to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:58.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe she got upset because\NI said her desperate need
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:12:01.60,Main,,0,0,0,,to seem superior was the\Nfunniest thing I'd ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:05.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] It's hopeless.\NThey'll never get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:07.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NLike cats and dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:13.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NWell, I tried. It's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.61,0:12:15.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I really thought it\Nmight end up working.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:17.32,Main,,0,0,0,,That what would work?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:19.20,Main,,0,0,0,,You know, how I fixed\Nit so that Hayama
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:23.20,Main,,0,0,0,,and Nishiyama went\Nto Animal Town together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:24.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought it would be\Na good chance for them
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:27.16,Main,,0,0,0,,to bond or at least get\Nto know each other better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.25,0:12:28.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw, that's sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:30.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Actually, it was\Nself-preservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.96,0:12:32.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Class is getting pretty\Nawkward with those two
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:34.42,Main,,0,0,0,,always at each other's throats.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:35.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.59,0:12:37.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Why can't you just get along?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:40.18,Main,,0,0,0,,You've got so much in common;\Nit should be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:41.59,Main,,0,0,0,,You know, it's funny...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:44.14,Main,,0,0,0,,That sounds a lot like something\NI said to you recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:49.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Finished the\NMega Ogre Rice Omelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:50.89,Main,,0,0,0,,What's for dessert?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:52.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHOP OWNER]\NThat's it. Time's up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.65,0:12:53.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Spoon down please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:55.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAJIME]\NAww...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:56.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I lost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:12:58.45,Main,,0,0,0,,She beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.24,0:13:02.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't think that you've\Nheard the last of me yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.16,0:13:03.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Futaba Odagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:06.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't forget this!\N[sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:08.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHOP OWNER]\NThanks for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:10.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Can't you get along?\NYou have so much in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:13.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Nope. Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:15.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NHayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:19.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[imitating guitar]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:28.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's start a band!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:31.10,Main,,0,0,0,,And why would we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.19,0:13:33.15,Main,,0,0,0,,'Cause it's the\Nseason of the arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:34.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NWhat are you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:36.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NHey! We're starting a band.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.61,0:13:37.78,Main,,0,0,0,,You wanna join?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:40.28,Main,,0,0,0,,You two look like\Nyou'd be musical.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:42.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Our band is gonna rule!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:43.74,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:47.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NWhat now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:51.96,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ River of Three Crossings. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:57.88,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ But I cannot find a way\Nto reach the other side. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:14:00.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] I didn't realize\Nyour sister could sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:02.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Her voice is almost hypnotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:08.51,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ I close my eyes\Nand dream. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:09.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:13.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Anybody else's ears\Nhurting, or is it just me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:15.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU (SONG)]\N♪ River of Three Crossings. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.98,0:14:18.86,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ But I have no coin to give. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:21.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to pick\Nthat flower up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:23.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Yamaji. I need you\Nto be my ladder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:24.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Wee!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:26.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU (SONG)]\N♪ River of Three Crossings. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:29.28,Main,,0,0,0,,--♪ River of Two Crossings. ♪\N--[YOKO] Go get it, Yu! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.37,0:14:31.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU (SONG)]\N♪ River of One Crossing. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:34.96,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ River of No Crossings." ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:39.96,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ River of sadness\Nand days forever lost. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:42.88,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ La, la, la, la,\Nla, laaaa, la." ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.97,0:14:44.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NYoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:45.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.63,0:14:46.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:49.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness you're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:51.27,Main,,0,0,0,,You had me really worried\Nfor a second there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:54.98,Main,,0,0,0,,What happened to you?\NDid you pass out or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:56.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NThat was strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:57.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Were those memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.15,0:14:58.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.57,0:15:01.28,Main,,0,0,0,,That was "River of Three\NCrossings," sung by Kou Hayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:02.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NSo depressing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:05.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Why sing about the river people\Ncross to reach the afterlife?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:06.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[KOU]\NOh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.45,0:15:07.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Haven't you ever\Njust started singing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:09.33,Main,,0,0,0,,without thinking about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:10.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I do it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:13.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Like when I'm cooking\Nor doing chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:15.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama, you know\Nwhat I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:16.88,Main,,0,0,0,,You sing songs\Ndedicated to Eternal
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.96,0:15:18.67,Main,,0,0,0,,when you're alone in\Nyour room, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:20.09,Main,,0,0,0,,No way! I don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:22.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Ooh! I wanna hear one!\NSing one for us, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:24.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you,\Nthere aren't any songs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:28.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama! Nishiyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.39,0:15:30.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop it! People are\Nstarting to stare.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.35,0:15:34.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO] Nishiyama! Nishiyama,\Nyeah! Nishiyama, whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:38.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama, hey! Nishiyama, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:40.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama got\Nso mad yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.11,0:15:41.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought she was\Ngonna punch someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:44.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I kinda felt bad for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:45.70,Main,,0,0,0,,After what you said\Nto her at Animal Town,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.78,0:15:47.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I find that pretty\Nhard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:49.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:50.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.08,0:15:52.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NYeah. It's Kondo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:55.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't think I've ever\Nsee her all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:58.08,Main,,0,0,0,,She's usually glued\Nto Nishiyama's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:06.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] She's all alone.\NI wonder what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.47,0:16:08.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Did she and Nishiyama\Nget into a fight
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.22,0:16:10.30,Main,,0,0,0,,because of what\Nhappened yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.39,0:16:12.85,Main,,0,0,0,,She's been abandoned\Nby her best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:14.06,Main,,0,0,0,,It breaks my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:15.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] But you always\Neat bread for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:18.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] I've told you before,\Nrice is my favorite food.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:19.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO]\NSeriously? Rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:20.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kondo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:22.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:24.15,Main,,0,0,0,,She's gonna have lunch with us\Ntoday if that's okay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:26.53,Main,,0,0,0,,She was walking around\Nlike a lost little puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:29.07,Main,,0,0,0,,So I figured I'd invite her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:30.95,Main,,0,0,0,,What a wonderful idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.62,0:16:34.08,Main,,0,0,0,,A jerk who would\Nabandon you like that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:35.75,Main,,0,0,0,,doesn't deserve your friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:37.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NWe'll be your friends now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:39.08,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:40.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Do you think\Nmaybe she's being
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:41.79,Main,,0,0,0,,a little too welcoming?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:45.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Miss Yoko does know a\Nthing or two about being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:48.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama's my best friend,\Nand she's not a jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:50.05,Main,,0,0,0,,She's actually really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.13,0:16:51.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Once you get to\Nknow her, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:55.39,Main,,0,0,0,,She just has a\Nvery fragile ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:57.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway,\Nwhy don't we eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:58.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Sound good?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:00.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NElementary school, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.94,0:17:02.90,Main,,0,0,0,,So you two have known\Neach other a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:03.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO]\NMm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.69,0:17:05.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Since the third grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.11,0:17:07.57,Main,,0,0,0,,We ended up in the same\Ngroup during a field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:09.24,Main,,0,0,0,,She was our group leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:11.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Whenever she saw me\Nstarting to fall behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.24,0:17:12.66,Main,,0,0,0,,she would come to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:14.28,Main,,0,0,0,,So you're saying\Nshe's always liked
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.37,0:17:15.79,Main,,0,0,0,,being the one in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.87,0:17:17.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.87,0:17:19.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I gotta admit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:22.58,Main,,0,0,0,,She wasn't always as\Ndifficult as she is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.67,0:17:24.09,Main,,0,0,0,,It's high school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:26.76,Main,,0,0,0,,You gotta learn\Nto go with the flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.84,0:17:29.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Plus, these days there's always\Nsomebody getting in her way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:31.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear. Do you mean me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:33.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:35.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] If Nishiyama\Ncould just be more careful
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:37.10,Main,,0,0,0,,about what she says out loud,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:39.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I bet she and Hayama\Ncould actually get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:41.39,Main,,0,0,0,,They have so much in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.48,0:17:42.81,Main,,0,0,0,,You could teach her a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.90,0:17:45.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I bet she could even be class\Nrepresentative someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.57,0:17:47.36,Main,,0,0,0,,But that's only if she\Ncould pretend to be nice
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:48.78,Main,,0,0,0,,the way that you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:49.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:52.65,Main,,0,0,0,,You could work on\Nthat too, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.74,0:17:55.08,Main,,0,0,0,,You come off so\Nprickly and snobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:57.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Try talking to the people\Nin your class sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:17:58.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:00.33,Main,,0,0,0,,The problem is\Nyou're too pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:02.75,Main,,0,0,0,,So it's your job to\Nstart conversations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.83,0:18:04.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Really? You think I'm pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.88,0:18:06.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, totally!\NIf a pretty girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:08.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NWhat the heck's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:10.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NIs she being nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.55,0:18:14.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Being mean?\NOr just plain oblivious?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:17.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Basically, you should\Ntry harder to talk to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:19.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NRight. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.14,0:18:23.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO]\NThanks a lot for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.27,0:18:25.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:28.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[SASAME]\NFutaba Odagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:32.61,Main,,0,0,0,,You beat my brother at\Na food challenge again,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.70,0:18:33.86,Main,,0,0,0,,didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.95,0:18:35.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[huffing]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:37.74,Main,,0,0,0,,To be fair, I didn't actually\Nknow we were competing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:41.04,Main,,0,0,0,,And you get to eat lunch with\NNishikawa every single day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:43.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Just the three of you,\Nlike some little clique!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.38,0:18:49.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know\Nwhat to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:50.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm just special.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:53.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Special? Special?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.06,0:19:01.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[SASAME yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:04.69,Main,,0,0,0,,She's an interesting one, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:08.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, you're pretty\Ninteresting yourself, Kondo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:10.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Ramen's best with\Npork, tons of veggies,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:11.44,Main,,0,0,0,,and a nice, runny egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.53,0:19:12.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Am I right, or am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:14.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:16.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:17.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I was hoping you would\Ncome with me somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.91,0:19:19.41,Main,,0,0,0,,if you're not busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:23.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[door opens]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:26.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello. Wait, I know her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.62,0:19:29.09,Main,,0,0,0,,You're never too old\Nfor cosplaying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.17,0:19:30.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, how could I forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:32.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama's friend\Nwho has no tact.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:33.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you can help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.05,0:19:35.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Kondo wants to pick out\Nsomething special
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.84,0:19:38.55,Main,,0,0,0,,for Nishiyama to\Nhelp them make up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:39.89,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "make up"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:42.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. I have just the thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:48.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NHere!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:51.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NWhy did you bring that out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.40,0:19:54.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NIt's something Nishiyama likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:56.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO]\NHey! I recognize that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.28,0:19:58.87,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the uniform Nishiyama\Nwore when she worked here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.95,0:20:01.16,Main,,0,0,0,,A cake, Sonobe!\NWe want a cake she likes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:02.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.49,0:20:03.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I gotta say, that was\Nreally funny, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.04,0:20:05.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I was\Nable to amuse you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.04,0:20:08.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it really true that\Nyou used to be a servant
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.17,0:20:10.50,Main,,0,0,0,,and you worked for\NNishikawa's family?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.59,0:20:11.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NIt is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:13.13,Main,,0,0,0,,So she was a\Nrich girl once,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:15.26,Main,,0,0,0,,just like everybody's\Nalways saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.34,0:20:17.34,Main,,0,0,0,,That explains a lot\Nabout her personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:19.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Like how overbearing\Nand stand-offish she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:22.68,Main,,0,0,0,,She really has no\Nfilter, does she?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:25.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Hope she doesn't\Ntry that with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:28.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] I think this is\Nreally big of you, Kondo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.02,0:20:30.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO]\NHuh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:32.11,Main,,0,0,0,,She's the one who\Nshould apologize
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.19,0:20:33.48,Main,,0,0,0,,for blowing things\Nout of proportion,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:35.36,Main,,0,0,0,,and yet here you are,\Ngoing out of your way
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:37.11,Main,,0,0,0,,to heal the rift between you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.19,0:20:38.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.49,0:20:40.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh, Yoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:44.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I think you\Nmisunderstood what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.04,0:20:47.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Kondo wasn't alone\Nbecause she and Nishiyama
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.16,0:20:48.87,Main,,0,0,0,,got into a fight or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.96,0:20:50.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama's sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.13,0:20:52.46,Main,,0,0,0,,So she had to stay home\Nfrom school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.55,0:20:58.05,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:20:59.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I... I just--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:01.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Well... I just assumed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:03.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO]\NHere. Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.81,0:21:05.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I sent her a ton of\Nemails this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:06.89,Main,,0,0,0,,to see how she was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:08.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:12.23,Main,,0,0,0,,But all the things I've said!\NI feel like an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.31,0:21:13.73,Main,,0,0,0,,It's all right.\NThese things happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.82,0:21:14.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.98,0:21:16.32,Main,,0,0,0,,It's kinda your fault, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:19.74,Main,,0,0,0,,You weren't all that clear\Nabout the situation, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:21.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NWhat's the deal with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.74,0:21:24.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Why did she suddenly stop\Nemailing me after lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.08,0:21:27.83,Main,,0,0,0,,She sent so many this\Nmorning I couldn't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.29,0:21:31.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[EL meows]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.54,0:21:35.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[meows]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.76,0:21:38.01,Main,,0,0,0,,My sweet little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.09,0:21:40.09,Main,,0,0,0,,You always know when I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.97,0:21:46.77,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ Eternal is your name, love. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.85,0:21:49.60,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ One that means\Nso much to me. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.68,0:21:53.23,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ E-T-E-R-N-A-L. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.86,0:21:56.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NKou was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.07,0:22:00.11,Main,,0,0,0,,She's singing a song\Ndedicated to her cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.19,0:22:02.32,Main,,0,0,0,,We finally get to hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.40,0:22:05.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you think we should\Ngo in or come back later?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.20,0:22:09.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's listen until she's done.\NIt's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.24,0:22:11.71,Main,,0,0,0,,--What?!\N--Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.79,0:22:14.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA (SONG)] ♪ R because\Nyou're really cute. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.71,0:22:17.96,Main,,0,0,0,,♪ N because you'll never leave.\NA for... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.93,0:23:50.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO]\NIt's Asako...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.47,0:23:52.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA] ...and Selina's\Npreview for the next episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.89,0:23:54.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA] I've had enough!\NJust do whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.60,0:23:55.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO]\NOh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.06,0:23:57.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, why don't you sing a\Ncharacter song or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.35,0:23:58.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.44,0:24:00.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONDO] Character song!\NCharacter song!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.52,0:24:03.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[NISHIYAMA]\NI... I guess I have no choice.
